text: ['3.1.6  Import controls', "3.39.  According  to  the  authorities,  Guyana's  import  control  regime  (including  prohibition, restriction and licensing) remained largely unchanged during the period under review."]

['3.2.6  Import controls', '3.34.  The basic framework for import controls (including prohibitions, restrictions, and licensing) has remained largely unchanged since the previous Review of HKC, apart from steps taken to align the regime more closely with international practices.']
